<div class="about-page">
    <h1>About SnipShare</h1>

    <p>SnipShare is a minimalist, open-source code snippet sharing platform built for developers who want to share code quickly without the hassle of creating accounts.</p>

    <h2>Features</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>No account required</li>
        <li>Syntax highlighting for popular languages</li>
        <li>Clean, distraction-free interface</li>
        <li>100% open source</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Open Source</h2>
    <p>We believe in transparency. Our entire codebase is available on GitHub for anyone to review, contribute to, or fork.</p>
    <a href="https://github.com/dreekos/SnipShare" class="btn btn-secondary" target="_blank">View on GitHub</a>

    <h2>Tech Stack</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Node.js + Express</li>
        <li>SQLite for storage</li>
        <li>EJS templates</li>
        <li>Vanilla JavaScript</li>
    </ul>
</div>

